title: Bassmasters to auction off a pheasant hunt!
content: The Borderline Bassmasters will be auctioning off a pheasant hunt for ten lucky hunters for November 21st at the Lantz Ranch. Proceeds will help fund members who qualified to fish at the Central Regionals for the South Dakota State Team. Bids can be called into DB'S Bait and Tackle at 842-2199. Bids will end October 31st.
